: 03/03/2025"}]}, {"date": "10-16-2024", "type": "Routine", "seats": "Food Service (Non-Profit)", "reportUrl": "https://ri.healthinspections.us/_templates/62/Restaurant/_report_full.cfm?inspID=5582882&domainID=62&userID=0&rtype=Restaurant&reportIDParent=0&SubType='&dsn=DHD_62&wguid=1367&wgunm=sysuser&wgdmn=630_2&logintime=%2200:00:00%20AM%22&public=1", "violations": []}, {"date": "10-05-2023", "type": "Routine", "seats": "Food Service (Non-Profit)", "reportUrl": "https://ri.healthinspections.us/_templates/62/Restaurant/_report_full.cfm?inspID=4160182&domainID=62&userID=0&rtype=Restaurant&reportIDParent=0&SubType='&dsn=DHD_62&wguid=1367&wgunm=sysuser&wgdmn=630_2&logintime=%2200:00:00%20AM%22&public=1", "violations": [{"item": 38, "code": "6-202.15", "severity": "C", "text": "The door to the outside, located in the back stairs , is not tight-fitting. Outer openings of a food establishment must be protected against the entry of insects and rodents by tight-fitting doors. New Violation. Correct By: 10/12/2023"}, {"item": 53, "code": "5-501.17", "severity": "C", "text": "The receptacle in the women's toilet room is lacking a cover. A toilet room used by females shall be provided with a covered receptacle for sanitary napkins. New Violation. Correct By: 10/05/2023"}, {"item": 54, "code": "5-501.115", "severity": "C", "text": "The outside dumpster is not covered. Receptacles and waste handling units for refuse, recyclables, and returnables shall be kept covered. New Violation. Correct By: 10/05/2023"}]}, {"date": "08-18-2023", "type": "Opening", "seats": "Food Service (Non-Profit)", "reportUrl": "https://ri.healthinspections.us/_templates/62/Restaurant/_report_full.cfm?inspID=4159570&domainID=62&userID=0&rtype=Restaurant&reportIDParent=0&SubType='&dsn=DHD_62&wguid=1367&wgunm=sysuser&wgdmn=630_2&logintime=%2200:00:00%20AM%22&public=1", "violations": []}]